@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<style>
    .custom-container {
        padding-top: 5%; /* Adjust this value to your preference */
    }
</style>
<div class="container custom-container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1>Welcome to Daddies International Banking Services</h1>
            <p>At Daddies International Banking Services, we're not your typical bank. We go above and beyond to redefine the banking experience, infusing it with a unique blend of expertise and humor. Our goal is simple: to empower our customers with financial knowledge while providing them with the tools and resources they need to succeed. We're not just about transactions; we're about building relationships and fostering trust. From personalized financial advice to cutting-edge digital banking solutions, we're committed to maximizing gains and delivering top-notch service every step of the way. At Daddies International Banking Services, your financial success is our priority, and we'll stop at nothing to ensure you achieve it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Our Mission</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Our mission is simple: to provide you with the tools and expertise you need to achieve maximum financial success. Whether you're saving for retirement, buying your dream home, or planning your next big adventure, we're here to help you every step of the way.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Our Values</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">At Daddies International Banking Services, we believe in transparency, integrity, and innovation. We strive to build long-lasting relationships with our customers based on trust and mutual respect. With us, you can rest assured that your financial future is in good hands.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card mb-4" >
                <div class="card-body" style="padding-top: -50px;">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Why Choose Us?</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">With so many banks out there, why should you choose Daddies International Banking Services? Here are just a few reasons:</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>Expert financial advice tailored to your needs</li>
                        <li>State-of-the-art online and mobile banking</li>
                        <li>Competitive rates and fees</li>
                        <li>A friendly and knowledgeable customer service team</li>
                        <li>A touch of humor to make banking fun!</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Our Commitment to You</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">When you bank with us, you're not just a customer – you're part of the Daddies family. We're committed to providing you with the highest level of service and support, ensuring that your financial goals become a reality. Your success is our success!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

</div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <div class="card custom-shadow" style="height: auto;">
                    <img src="~/Images/buffImage2.png" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center">Banking and Working Out</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">"Investing in your financial health is like working out. It may be challenging at first, but the long-term benefits are worth the effort." - D.I.B.S</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


